de:"Vielen Dank f\u00fcr deine Hilfe! Dies sind deine Speicherdaten. Bitte alles ausw\u00e4hlen, kopieren und per E-Mail an dev@airapport.com senden.",en:"Appreciate your help! This is your save data. Please, select it all (long press -> select all), copy (long press -> copy) and send in email to the developer: dev@airapport.com",es:"\u00a1Aprecio tu ayuda! Estos son sus datos de guardado. Por favor, seleccione todo (pulsaci\u00f3n larga -> seleccionar todo), copiar (pulsaci\u00f3n larga -> copiar) y enviar correo electr\u00f3nico al desarrollador: dev@airapport.com",
fr:"J'appr\u00e9cie votre aide ! Ceci est votre sauvegarde des donn\u00e9es. S'il vous pla\u00eet, s\u00e9lectionnez tout (appui long -> S\u00e9lectionner tout), copier (appui long -> copier) et envoyer par courrier \u00e9lectronique au d\u00e9veloppeur : dev@airapport.com",hu:"K\u00f6sz\u00f6n\u00f6m a seg\u00edts\u00e9ged! Ezek a ment\u00e9si adataid. K\u00e9rlek v\u00e1laszd ki az eg\u00e9szet (tartsd nyomva-> \u00f6sszes kiv\u00e1laszt\u00e1sa), m\u00e1sold ki (hosszan nyomva tart\u00e1s -> m\u00e1sol\u00e1s) \u00e9s k\u00fcldd el e-mailben a fejleszt\u0151nek: dev@airapport.com",
id:"Hargai bantuan Anda! Ini adalah data simpanan Anda. Silakan pilih semuanya (tekan lama -> pilih semua), salin (tekan lama -> salin) dan kirim email ke pengembang: dev@airapport.com",it:"Apprezzo il tuo aiuto! Questi sono i tuoi dati di salvataggio. Si prega di selezionare tutto (premere a lungo -> Seleziona tutto), copiare (premere a lungo -> copia) e inviare un'email allo sviluppatore: dev@airapport.com",ja:"\u3054\u5354\u529b\u611f\u8b1d\u3057\u307e\u3059\uff01\u3053\u308c\u304c\u3042\u306a\u305f\u306e\u30bb\u30fc\u30d6\u30c7\u30fc\u30bf\u3067\u3059\u3002\u3059\u3079\u3066\u9078\u629e\uff08\u9577\u62bc\u3057 -> \u3059\u3079\u3066\u9078\u629e\uff09\u3057\u3066\u30b3\u30d4\u30fc\uff08\u9577\u62bc\u3057 -> \u30b3\u30d4\u30fc\uff09\u3057\u3001\u958b\u767a\u8005\u306b\u30e1\u30fc\u30eb\u3067\u9001\u4fe1\u3057\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044\uff1adev@airapport.com",
